'''Paul Newman''' is an American accountant, currently the [[Clark W. Thompson (Texas politician)|Clark W. Thompson]] Jr. Chair in Accounting at [[University of Texas at Austin]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mccombs.utexas.edu/Directory/Profiles/Newman-Donald |title=Paul Newman |publisher=utexas.edu |accessdate=December 11, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.worldcat.org/identities/viaf-211983846/ |title=Newman, Donald Paul |publisher=worldcat.org |accessdate=December 11, 2016}}</ref>

